            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Décharné, de haillons vêtu,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Fou de fièvre, au coin d'un impasse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Jean Misère s'est abattu.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "«Douleur, dit-il, n'es-tu pas lasse ?»",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Ça ne finira donc jamais ?…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Décharné, de haillons vêtu,\nFou de fièvre, au coin d'un impasse,\nJean Misère s'est abattu.\n«Douleur, dit-il, n'es-tu pas lasse ?»\nÇa ne finira donc jamais ?…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Pas un astre et pas un ami !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "La place est déserte et perdue.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "S'il faisait sec, j'aurais dormi,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Il pleut de la neige fondue.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Ça ne finira donc jamais ?…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pas un astre et pas un ami !\nLa place est déserte et perdue.\nS'il faisait sec, j'aurais dormi,\nIl pleut de la neige fondue.\nÇa ne finira donc jamais ?…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Est-ce la fin, mon vieux pavé ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Tu vois : ni gîte, ni pitance,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Ah ! la poche au fiel a crevé ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Je voudrais vomir l'existence.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Ça ne finira donc jamais ?…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Est-ce la fin, mon vieux pavé ?\nTu vois : ni gîte, ni pitance,\nAh ! la poche au fiel a crevé ;\nJe voudrais vomir l'existence.\nÇa ne finira donc jamais ?…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Je fus bon ouvrier tailleur.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Vieux, que suis-je ? une loque immonde.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "C'est l'histoire du travailleur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Depuis que notre monde est monde.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Ça ne finira donc jamais ?…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je fus bon ouvrier tailleur.\nVieux, que suis-je ? une loque immonde.\nC'est l'histoire du travailleur,\nDepuis que notre monde est monde.\nÇa ne finira donc jamais ?…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Maigre salaire et nul repos,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Il faut qu'on s'y fasse ou qu'on crève,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Bonnets carrés et chassepots",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Ne se mettent jamais en grève.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Ça ne finira donc jamais ?…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Maigre salaire et nul repos,\nIl faut qu'on s'y fasse ou qu'on crève,\nBonnets carrés et chassepots\nNe se mettent jamais en grève.\nÇa ne finira donc jamais ?…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Malheur ! ils nous font la leçon,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Ils prêchent l'ordre et la famille ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Leur guerre a tué mon garçon,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Leur luxe a débauché ma fille !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Ça ne finira donc jamais ?…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Malheur ! ils nous font la leçon,\nIls prêchent l'ordre et la famille ;\nLeur guerre a tué mon garçon,\nLeur luxe a débauché ma fille !\nÇa ne finira donc jamais ?…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "De ces détrousseurs inhumains,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "L'Église bénit les sacoches ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Et leur bon Dieu nous tient les mains",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Pendant qu'on fouille dans nos poches.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Ça ne finira donc jamais ?…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "De ces détrousseurs inhumains,\nL'Église bénit les sacoches ;\nEt leur bon Dieu nous tient les mains\nPendant qu'on fouille dans nos poches.\nÇa ne finira donc jamais ?…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Un jour, le Ciel s'est éclairé,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Le soleil a lui dans mon bouge ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "J'ai pris l'arme d'un fédéré",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Et j'ai suivi le drapeau rouge.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Ça ne finira donc jamais ?…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Un jour, le Ciel s'est éclairé,\nLe soleil a lui dans mon bouge ;\nJ'ai pris l'arme d'un fédéré\nEt j'ai suivi le drapeau rouge.\nÇa ne finira donc jamais ?…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Mais, par mille on nous coucha bas ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "C'était sinistre au clair de lune ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Quand on m'a retiré du tas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "J'ai crié : Vive la Commune !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Ça ne finira donc jamais ?…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais, par mille on nous coucha bas ;\nC'était sinistre au clair de lune ;\nQuand on m'a retiré du tas,\nJ'ai crié : Vive la Commune !\nÇa ne finira donc jamais ?…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Adieu, martyrs de Satory,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Adieu, nos châteaux en Espagne !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Ah ! mourons !… ce monde est pourri ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "On en sort comme on sort d'un bagne.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Ça ne finira donc jamais ?…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Adieu, martyrs de Satory,\nAdieu, nos châteaux en Espagne !\nAh ! mourons !… ce monde est pourri ;\nOn en sort comme on sort d'un bagne.\nÇa ne finira donc jamais ?…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "A la morgue on coucha son corps,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Et tous les jours, dalles de pierre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Vous étalez de nouveaux morts :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Les Otages de la misère !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Ça ne finira donc jamais ?…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "A la morgue on coucha son corps,\nEt tous les jours, dalles de pierre,\nVous étalez de nouveaux morts :\nLes Otages de la misère !\nÇa ne finira donc jamais ?…"
        }
    ],
